## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7462d-102">在 WPF 应用程序启动时，使用类在启动窗口或初始屏幕中显示 <xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen> 图像。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-102">Use the <xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen> class to show an image in a startup window, or *splash screen*, when a WPF application starts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7462d-103"><xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen.Show%2A>调用方法以显示初始屏幕。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-103">Call the <xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen.Show%2A> method to display the splash screen.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7462d-104"><xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen.Close%2A>调用方法以关闭初始屏幕。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-104">Call the <xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen.Close%2A> method to close the splash screen.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7462d-105">指定要在<xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen>构造函数中使用的映像。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-105">Specify the image to use in the <xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen> constructor.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7462d-106"><xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen>类可以显示 Windows 映像组件（WIC）支持的任何图像格式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-106">The <xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen> class can display any image format that is supported by the Windows Imaging Component (WIC).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7462d-107">例如，可以使用 BMP、GIF、JPEG、PNG 或 TIFF 格式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-107">For example, you can use the BMP, GIF, JPEG, PNG, or TIFF format.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7462d-108">如果图像是 PNG 文件，并且它包含 alpha 通道，则将使用 alpha 通道中定义的透明度呈现图像。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-108">If the image is a PNG file and it includes an alpha channel, the image is rendered using the transparency defined in the alpha channel.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7462d-109">你不能在随后由你的代码添加的初始屏幕中包含占位符文本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-109">You cannot include placeholder text in the splash screen that is later added by your code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7462d-110">如果要在初始屏幕中包含文本，则必须将其添加到图像文件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-110">If you want to include text in the splash screen, you must add it to the image file.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="7462d-111">无需编写任何代码即可显示初始屏幕。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-111">It is not necessary to write any code to display a splash screen.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7462d-112">[!INCLUDE[vs_orcas_long](~/includes/vs-orcas-long-md.md)]从 SP1 开始，你可以使用默认设置快速配置初始屏幕。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-112">Starting in [!INCLUDE[vs_orcas_long](~/includes/vs-orcas-long-md.md)] SP1, you can quickly configure a splash screen with default settings.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7462d-113">有关详细信息，请参阅[如何：将初始屏幕添加到 WPF 应用程序](~/docs/framework/wpf/app-development/how-to-add-a-splash-screen-to-a-wpf-application.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-113">For more information, see [How to: Add a Splash Screen to a WPF Application](~/docs/framework/wpf/app-development/how-to-add-a-splash-screen-to-a-wpf-application.md).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7462d-114"><xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen>类在应用程序启动后尽快显示初始屏幕。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-114">The <xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen> class displays the splash screen as soon as possible after the application is started.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7462d-115">在创建 WPF 应用程序实例之前，将使用本机代码显示初始屏幕。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-115">The splash screen is displayed by using native code, before the WPF application instance is created.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7462d-116">屏幕的中心将显示初始屏幕。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-116">The splash screen is displayed in the center of the screen.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7462d-117">加载应用程序后，初始屏幕会淡化。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-117">When the application is loaded, the splash screen fades.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7462d-118">在编译应用程序时，该图像将作为托管资源嵌入到程序集中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-118">When your application is compiled, the image is embedded as a managed resource in the assembly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7462d-119">如果对应用程序进行了本地化，则会将该图像嵌入到已本地化的附属 DLL 中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-119">If the application is localized, the image is embedded in the localized satellite DLL.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="7462d-120"><xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen>类在部分信任环境中不可用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-120">The <xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen> class is not available in partial trust.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="7462d-121"><xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen>类不能用于 XAML 浏览器应用程序（xbap），因为它们使用不同的启动体系结构。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7462d-121">The <xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen> class cannot be used in XAML Browser Applications (XBAPs), because they use a different startup architecture.</span></span>  
  
   
  
